{"tid":975763,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"超商失竊狗罐頭　驚！竊賊竟然是汪星人","createTime":"2019-01-10T02:09:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-10T06:49:34.000Z","uid":32511,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"5dd9aea02791d5e0d9b6a77cde5164b4aed8d837","tid":975763,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T02:09:50.000Z","msg":"竊賊是狗不是人！新北市三重區一家連鎖便利商店，日前盤點遺失一罐西莎狗罐頭，經調閱店內監視器畫面，驚見竊賊不是「人」而是一隻狗，店家無奈自認倒楣，將影片上傳臉書《爆料公社》，標題寫下「欸～付錢呀！」<br />\n <br />\n影片一出吸引不少網友按讚，有網友看完影片在下留言打趣的說「這小偷職業級的」、還開玩笑的說「哇靠～還會挑勒」、「自選西莎罐頭」、「自助餐逆？」甚至說「哈哈哈，自己的罐罐自己來」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Cy1dOjy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCy1dOjy.png&h=52f85afd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ee5090645a5521e77bd209ca74178355e202b84d","tid":975763,"uid":70832,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T02:10:53.000Z","msg":"應該有人教<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad4de885c9f19503ab246559f12981b2f5347b87","tid":975763,"uid":45368,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T02:12:12.000Z","msg":"隻台狗又幾醒喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7aed8e08c94aa80e06b56ce14beb62a1f3c6d696","tid":975763,"uid":37258,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ee5090645a5521e77bd209ca74178355e202b84d","tid":975763,"uid":70832,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T02:10:53.000Z","msg":"應該有人教<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T03:57:04.000Z","msg":"以後唔洗買糧 佢肚餓自己識搵食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff91884f5cea541c0050fd24e0a2b63d8ec5ac0e","tid":975763,"uid":21917,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T03:58:41.000Z","msg":"真係訓練有素<img src=